parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic power steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock up or become difficult to turn, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The steering wheel suddenly locks up
the steering wheel becomes stiff and difficult to turn
the "Steering Assist Fault
Service Required" message appears on the instrument panel
the vehicle pulls to one side
the power steering assist indicator illuminates
and the vehicle becomes difficult to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear back up camera can increase the risk of accidents, especially when reversing, as the driver may not be able to see obstacles or pedestrians behind the vehicle.
symptoms: The rear back up camera fails to display an image
or the image is distorted or unclear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column control module can cause the horn to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or increase the risk of accidents, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: The horn does not sound when pressed
or the horn sounds intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and can also cause discomfort and inconvenience to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The heat or radio blasts unexpectedly
the doors lock and unlock sporadically
and the system is unpredictable and unresponsive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water leaks and retention can cause electrical system failures, corrosion, and damage to the vehicle's interior, which can lead to accidents or increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Water leaks from the moon roof area
water retention in the doors
and water accumulation in the floorboards.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the moon roof can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and can also cause discomfort and inconvenience to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The moon roof opens or closes unexpectedly
and the sun screen does not close properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the speedometer can increase the risk of accidents, especially when driving in heavy rain or low-visibility conditions, as the driver may not be able to accurately gauge their speed.
symptoms: The speedometer fails to illuminate or display the correct speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls upon acceleration
the vehicle will not start
the vehicle makes an abnormal clicking sound
the air conditioner turns off independently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump relay module can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to potential accidents, especially on busy highways, and leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or does not start
the fuel pump control module fails
the fuel pump relay module is broken.
